        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks CL for his favourable remarks to the Geological Section of the BAAS concerning the forthcoming publication of the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>. Hopes CL will accept his view of species.</p>  
<p>Comments on CL’s paper ["On the occurrence of works of human art in post-Pliocene deposits", <hi rend="italic">Rep. BAAS</hi> 29 (1859): 93–5].</p> 
